WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.466 --> 00:00:02.066
Finally, it's quiet.

2
00:00:02.100 --> 00:00:03.166
Since ancient times,

3
00:00:03.166 --> 00:00:05.766
those who dare to plot rebellion are usually very bold.

4
00:00:06.066 --> 00:00:09.000
Why does Duke Duan act so openly and without concealment?

5
00:00:09.866 --> 00:00:11.300
Duke Duan, the Taoist priest.

6
00:00:11.766 --> 00:00:13.200
Elder Brother, you see,

7
00:00:13.300 --> 00:00:16.700
I was just making a joke.

8
00:00:16.700 --> 00:00:18.566
Being able to make Duke Duan speechless

9
00:00:18.566 --> 00:00:20.600
shows he has some real skill.

10
00:00:20.766 --> 00:00:22.600
No wonder he is the Emperor’s brother.

11
00:00:22.600 --> 00:00:25.433
His words are even sharper.

12
00:00:33.333 --> 00:00:35.900
Are you sure you want to act during the banquet?

13
00:00:36.133 --> 00:00:38.433
The Empress Dowager and the Emperor are not fools.

14
00:00:38.466 --> 00:00:41.366
If we’re discovered, we’re finished.

15
00:00:42.200 --> 00:00:44.700
Don’t worry, I’ve already made arrangements.

16
00:00:44.700 --> 00:00:46.700
Once Princess Loulan is dead,

17
00:00:46.766 --> 00:00:48.400
Loulan will definitely be in turmoil.

18
00:00:48.566 --> 00:00:52.000
Even if they don’t fight, the chaos will ensue.

19
00:00:52.366 --> 00:00:54.900
You just need to stir up trouble in his harem.

20
00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:58.966
I don’t believe I won’t find an opportunity.

21
00:00:58.966 --> 00:01:00.400
It’s easier said than done.

22
00:01:00.400 --> 00:01:02.033
I’ve been demoted.

23
00:01:02.133 --> 00:01:04.300
I feel like the Emperor might have discovered something.

24
00:01:04.300 --> 00:01:07.200
If he finds out about our relationship,

25
00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:08.366
we’ll be...

26
00:01:09.266 --> 00:01:10.666
That day will not come.

27
00:01:11.100 --> 00:01:14.866
Who is that Rong Fei you mentioned?

28
00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:18.966
She appeared during the snowstorm.

29
00:01:18.966 --> 00:01:21.566
I’m still unmarried because of her.

30
00:01:22.266 --> 00:01:23.833
She does have some influence.

31
00:01:23.966 --> 00:01:26.200
She can affect your standing with the Emperor.

32
00:01:27.366 --> 00:01:28.833
If she argues with you,

33
00:01:29.166 --> 00:01:30.266
don’t worry.

34
00:01:30.266 --> 00:01:32.100
She won’t last long.

35
00:01:33.600 --> 00:01:34.766
I’ve already made preparations.

36
00:01:37.266 --> 00:01:38.966
They are keeping an eye on me.
